---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="アースカラー — 地域おこし協力隊DAO">
  <div class="earth">
    <!-- Nav -->
    <nav class="nav">
      <div class="nav-logo">
        <span class="nav-dot"></span>
        地域おこし協力隊DAO
      </div>
      <a href="#join" class="nav-cta">参加する</a>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-texture"></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="hero-tag">Community for Local Revitalization</p>
        <h1>土地の声を聴き、<br />人をつなぎ、<br />未来を耕す。</h1>
        <div class="hero-bottom">
          <p>地域おこし協力隊DAOは、全国の協力隊員と地域をWeb3でつなぐコミュニティです。一人ひとりの挑戦が、地域全体の力になる。</p>
          <div class="hero-scroll">
            <span>Scroll</span>
            <div class="scroll-line"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-img" style="background-color: #d4c5a0;"></div>
        <div class="feature-text">
          <span class="feature-num">01</span>
          <h2>知恵を共有する</h2>
          <p>地方移住、活動報告、資金調達のノウハウ。各地の経験がコミュニティの共有知になり、次の挑戦者の道しるべになる。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature reverse">
        <div class="feature-img" style="background-color: #8a9a7b;"></div>
        <div class="feature-text">
          <span class="feature-num">02</span>
          <h2>地域を越えて協働する</h2>
          <p>北海道の漁村と四国の山間部。離れていても共通の課題がある。DAOを通じて、地域横断のプロジェクトが生まれる。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-img" style="background-color: #c4956a;"></div>
        <div class="feature-text">
          <span class="feature-num">03</span>
          <h2>持続可能な仕組みを作る</h2>
          <p>活動が個人に依存しない。DAOのガバナンスにより、コミュニティ自体が自律的に成長し続ける仕組みを設計。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Quote -->
    <section class="quote">
      <div class="quote-inner">
        <blockquote>
          「この土地に来て初めて、<br />自分の居場所を見つけた気がした」
        </blockquote>
        <cite>— 地域おこし協力隊員の声</cite>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About -->
    <section class="about">
      <div class="about-inner">
        <div class="about-header">
          <span class="about-tag">About the DAO</span>
          <h2>地域おこし協力隊DAO<br />ができること</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="about-card">
            <div class="about-card-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
                <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" />
                <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87" />
                <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>コミュニティ</h3>
            <p>全国の隊員がオンラインでつながり、日々の悩みや成功を共有できる場</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-card">
            <div class="about-card-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z" />
                <path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>ナレッジベース</h3>
            <p>活動のノウハウ・事例を蓄積。先輩隊員の知恵を次世代へ</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-card">
            <div class="about-card-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                <path d="M2 12h20" />
                <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Web3 / DAO</h3>
            <p>分散型の意思決定。トークンを活用した新しい地域経済モデルの実験</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-card">
            <div class="about-card-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z" />
                <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>地域プロジェクト</h3>
            <p>複数地域をまたいだ協働プロジェクトの立ち上げ・支援</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section id="join" class="cta">
      <div class="cta-texture"></div>
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>地域に根を張り、<br />ともに育てよう。</h2>
        <p>地域おこし協力隊の現役隊員、OB/OG、地域に関わりたいすべての方へ。</p>
        <a href="#" class="cta-button">コミュニティに参加する</a>
        <span class="cta-org">Powered by 株式会社あるやうむ</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <a href="/" class="back-link">← デザイン一覧に戻る</a>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .earth {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    color: #3a3228;
    background: #f5f0e8;
  }

  /* Nav */
  .nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 48px;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .nav-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #8B6914;
  }

  .nav-cta {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 8px 24px;
    border: 1px solid #3a3228;
    border-radius: 100px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .nav-cta:hover {
    background: #3a3228;
    color: #f5f0e8;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding: 0 48px 80px;
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(165deg, #e8dcc8 0%, #d4c5a0 40%, #c4a265 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-texture {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.06;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-tag {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(58, 50, 40, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    color: #2a2218;
  }

  .hero-bottom {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .hero-bottom p {
    max-width: 480px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: rgba(58, 50, 40, 0.7);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .hero-scroll {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .hero-scroll span {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(58, 50, 40, 0.4);
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(58, 50, 40, 0.2);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .scroll-line::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -100%;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: #3a3228;
    animation: scroll-anim 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes scroll-anim {
    0% { top: -100%; }
    100% { top: 100%; }
  }

  /* Features */
  .features {
    padding: 120px 48px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 120px;
  }

  .feature {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .feature.reverse {
    direction: rtl;
  }

  .feature.reverse > * {
    direction: ltr;
  }

  .feature-img {
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    border-radius: 8px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .feature-img::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.8' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.15;
    mix-blend-mode: overlay;
  }

  .feature-num {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #8B6914;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }

  .feature-text h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .feature-text p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #777;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Quote */
  .quote {
    padding: 120px 48px;
    background: #3a3228;
    color: #f5f0e8;
  }

  .quote-inner {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    line-height: 2;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  cite {
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.4);
  }

  /* About */
  .about {
    padding: 120px 48px;
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-tag {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8B6914;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .about-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .about-card {
    padding: 32px 24px;
    background: rgba(139, 105, 20, 0.04);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .about-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .about-card-icon {
    color: #8B6914;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .about-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .about-card p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #888;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta {
    padding: 160px 48px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f5f0e8 0%, #e8dcc8 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-texture {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.04;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cta > .cta-content > p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 18px 56px;
    background: #8B6914;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(139, 105, 20, 0.3);
  }

  .cta-org {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 32px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #bbb;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #999;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(58, 50, 40, 0.1);
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: #3a3228;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
    .hero { padding: 0 24px 60px; }
    .hero-scroll { display: none; }
    .features { padding: 80px 24px; gap: 80px; }
    .feature, .feature.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      direction: ltr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .quote { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .about { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .cta { padding: 80px 24px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
